
It's simple code for displaying how to access C functions in nodejs using javascript.
First run c code and using it in nodejs.


run make start, the Makefile will automatically recompile any changes 


in Linux/Ubuntu:
sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y build-essential manpages-dev
sudo apt install -y python3-dev

in Windows:
npm install --global windows-build-tools



run in terminal:
make clean
make install
make start

